 10. Paste as Plain Text Toggle ⭐ LOW

 WordPress has "Paste as text" mode.

 What's Missing:
 - Pasting from Word/web keeps (sometimes unwanted) formatting
 - No way to paste plain text only

 Implementation:
 - Add toggle button for "Paste as plain text"
 - When enabled, strip all HTML on paste

 ---
 11. Block/Element Inspector ⭐ LOW

 WordPress Gutenberg shows block settings in sidebar.

 What's Missing:
 - No way to see/edit current element's classes
 - No CSS class picker for selected block

 Implementation:
 - Sidebar panel showing current block type
 - Class input field
 - Quick-add buttons for common blog classes

