 WordPress shows "Draft saved" status.

 What's Missing:
 - No visual indicator of save status
 - No auto-save functionality in editor itself

 Implementation:
 - Add status text: "Saved" / "Unsaved changes"
 - Optional: Auto-save to localStorage as backup

